Class AsyncMap<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.vertx.mutiny.core.shareddata.AsyncMap<K,V>

  • public class AsyncMap<K,V>
extends Object
    An asynchronous map.

    AsyncMap does not allow null to be used as a key or value.
